# AstroDefense

## Project Description
AstroDefense is a Java-based space shooter game where the player controls a spaceship, destroys asteroids/enemies, collects power-ups, and tries to survive while managing health and shields.

## Features
- Player movement controls
- Shooting mechanics
- Enemy/asteroid objects
- Collision detection
- Health and shield system
- Power-ups
- Timer system
- Sprite/image assets
- Score tracking

## Technologies Used
- Java
- Java Swing
- IntelliJ IDEA
- BufferedImage / ImageIO for graphics

## How to Run
1. Open the project in IntelliJ IDEA
2. Make sure all image/audio assets are located in the correct folders
3. Run the main Java class

## Controls
- Arrow Keys / WASD: Move spaceship
- Spacebar: Shoot

